### 23. Error Test - Create Contact Without Customer ID
POST {{baseUrl}}/contacts
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Invalid Contact",
  "email": "invalid@test.com"
}

> {%
